	   <tr><td colspan=2>for 1hs at your level then there are some nice claws...Icetooth claws 11/29 at about 300pp and Icepaw war claw 9/24 at about 450pp. For 2hs there are some very cheap options....Axe of the Iron Back 16/37 for about 80pp and when you reach level 20 Drakkel forged bastard sword for 100pp 20/45. And just a piece of advice about agro...some posts here are missleading. 1hs will create more agro than a 2hs weapon unless the 2hs weapon is greatly superior in dmg over time...so 1hs and a shield is the way to go when tanking..and 2hs when being the number 2 tank<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
