	   <tr><td colspan=2>Interesting.&nbsp;&nbsp;Im not stating that one way is better than another, but I would recommend, &amp; actually do, the exact opposite of what you recommended.  When I am the MA, I would generally use Ebon Mace (1HB) just SO that I can use my shield (inc AC--take less damage).  When I am not the MA, however, I would use a 2HS (Strength of Grodan perhaps), as I will not be taking much dmg.<br><br>Keep in mind, however, this assumes that I am NOT VERY concerned with the MOB casting spells.  If that is the case, I will almost always use a 1H weapon &amp; shield to bash.<br><br>Lunatic<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
