	   <tr><td colspan=2>This is my take, your an Iksar so you start off with a basic weapon, but that khuri (I think thats what its called) can become an awesome weapon by doing the quest to upgrade it.&nbsp;&nbsp;Having said that I would pick up a set of Icetooth claws 11/29 1hs pretty good weapon for around that coin, at least on my server, you could probably get them cheaper depending on how long the guy/gal has been auctioning. <br><br>Alternatively you could also try to pick up a cheap blunt weapon, I think a blackjack 7/21 1hb goes for about that same about amount of coin and the 1hb weapon will prepare you for the time when you can get Mace of the Shadowed Soul 19/29 10int 1hb sk only.<br><br>I would suggest pick up a piercing 2hs and 2hb weapon when you can to work those weapon skills too. Be prepared for any weapon that may fall in your lap. Nothing sucks more than to have an uber weapon that you have no skill in.  Also check this site out for details on your Iksar SK Dreadscale quest armor.<br><br>May the hate of Innoruuk be with you follower of Cazic Thule!!<br>&nbsp;<br>Cannis 51st Ranger<br>Razer 44th Sk<br>Jeetkundo 20th Monk<br>Mikaraz 27th Warrior<br>Taranthian 30th Necro</td></tr>
